OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh west to northwest winds
OL,6,Fbringing showers across the area
OL,7,Ftoday. Outbreaks ranging from frequent
OL,8,Fin western Central and Tayside, and
OL,9,Fisolated around the coast, where the
OL,10,Fbest of the limited brighter spells
OL,11,Fappear.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,14,Ffurther showers, these focused across
OL,15,Fthe north. Clear spells developing
OL,16,Fovernight, particularly in the Central
OL,17,FBelt where showers die out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
