OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,6,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,7,Fwith the Central Belt particularly
OL,8,Ffavoured and warm. However, some early
OL,9,Fshowers possible in the far north.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMost
OL,12,Fdry during Monday, with sunshine
OL,13,Fturning hazy for the afternoon.
OL,14,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,15,Fcrossing the area from the southwest
OL,16,Ffrom late Monday and through Tuesday
OL,17,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
